    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a YANG data model for configuring and managing routing policies in a vendor-neutral way.  The model provides a generic routing policy framework that can be extended for specific routing protocols using the YANG 'augment' mechanism.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
